item.description: Aloha! We are passionate about summer, sunshine, ocean and fashion. Our online operations are on the island of Oahu, Hawaii, so we often get distracted with beaches, epic waves and year around sunshine. Check out our product line that is a blend of the "Carioca Beach Fashion" of Rio de Janeiro, Brazil and the "Aloha Spirit" of Hawaii. Follow our blog and like us on Facebook to get the special deals offered only to our island Ohana!
